title: 678-Top AI Services for 2025-sudev
summary: The speaker shares insights from their experience building AI systems, guiding viewers on which AI solutions are profitable to sell (focusing on quick customer ROI) and which to avoid. It highlights effective services for enhancing sales processes.
latentAbility: Provides a checklist for evaluating the profitability potential of an AI service idea.

questions.text: According to the video, what is a key factor for an AI service to be profitable?
options: It must use the newest AI model
It should be free for users
It should offer a quick return on investment (ROI) for the customer
It needs to be completely automated
questions.correct: It should offer a quick return on investment (ROI) for the customer

questions.text: What is the main benefit highlighted for the effective AI services discussed?
options: They are the cheapest to build
They work for every type of business
